1176
01:53:23.783 --> 01:53:25.368
Samo sam smislio šalu.

1177
01:53:44.553 --> 01:53:46.555
Da li biste mi je ispričali?

1178
01:53:52.728 --> 01:53:54.354
Ne biste je shvatili.

1179
01:54:06.491 --> 01:54:08.159
To je život

1180
01:54:09.786 --> 01:54:12.705
I ma kako bio smešan

1181
01:54:14.165 --> 01:54:16.876
Neke baš raduje

1182
01:54:17.043 --> 01:54:18.878
Kada zgaze san

1183
01:54:20.213 --> 01:54:23.883
Ali ja ne dam
Ne dam da me tišti


1184
